(firstQuint)Study to Determine the Efficacy of Adalimumab in the Treatment of Cutaneous Sarcoidosis.

 The primary objective of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of adalimumab for the treatment of cutaneous sarcoidosis.

 A secondary objective is to study gene expression in sarcoidosis.

